{"tid":1035022,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多個人成日俾人當move on既踏板","createTime":"2019-02-24T10:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T02:01:41.000Z","uid":150698,"like":52,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ad3b47a3641d6452b35541aeca81401163843ced","tid":1035022,"uid":150698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:52:45.000Z","msg":"難聽啲講啫係水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你既作用就係陪伴佢渡過個失戀期<br />\n冇咁sad啦<br />\n發現唔係好鐘意你啦<br />\n發現你對佢好會內疚<br />\n<br />\n又或者之前太hurt<br />\n怕你既好只係一刻<br />\n之後又會似個佢個ex咁對你衰<br />\n<br />\n比較完一輪就bye 9 bye<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我就睇化左<br />\n不過回望下真係覺得自己柒下柒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個確定左情侶關係就一定all in既人表示<br />\n你班仆街仔要死死遠小小<br />\n唔鐘意人唔好搞人<br />\n<br />\n俾你班人搞到啲女仔對愛情冇曬信心<br />\n唔好嘈之後識唔到好女仔<br />\n<br />\n啲好女仔咪俾你班以為自私撚玩到絕曬種<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小妹回望自己咁多年俾人玩弄感情既經驗<br />\n發現我自己有啲特質吸引同會令一個人變成仆街<br />\n<br />\n慘到一個地步 <br />\n依加由自卑變成自信<br />\n<br />\n咩都睇化曬<br />\n<br />\n有時候啲仆街呢<br />\n其實只係對你仆街啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 單身 有幾個人追（絕已拒 冇收兵<br />\n表示感覺良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6521ca501ff91e95b48b852338ad2c38562bcb","tid":1035022,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7180ff1c4f47291a52b2eece2d6c724176292ad","tid":1035022,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e298e395cc3d4cfbe068e2e53fa33cf6e4a92e","tid":1035022,"uid":43329,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,